{
  "texts": [
    "This paper provided a comprehensive review of recent deep learning development in WPPs.",
    "It covered more than 140 recent WPP studies with advanced deep learning from two perspectives: WPP formulations and WPP methods.",
    "First, different developments in WPP formulations including the new designs of inputs, new settings of outputs, and new application of evaluation metrics reported in recent WPP studies were summarized.",
    "The evolution of input designs was propelled by the broader availability of input sources and an increased interest in leveraging highdimensional data for WPPs.",
    "Early data-driven studies mostly considered one source of input, either historical SCADA or NWP data."
  ]
}